WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.500
Hi, my name is Captain Pankaj Sabarwal

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:09.000
and I am giving this testimony for the software development.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:14.000
I got it done via ReinSoft company,

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:19.500
Mr. Manpreet and Ms. Tanu were handling my software.

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:24.500
I should say that they developed a fantastic

00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:29.500
certificate generation and verification software

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:33.000
for my maritime training institute.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:38.000
Both of them were very professional and very supportive

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:43.500
and I highly recommend them for your software development work.

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:46.000
Thanks.
